He has twice received the Pulitizer Prize for Biography with the most recent in 2002 for John Adams (Simon 
Mr. McCullough has also been honored with the National Book Foundation Distinguished Contribution to American Letters Award and is twice winner of the National Book Award and the Francis Parkman Prize.
He lives in West Tisbury, Massachusetts.
